Cellular Nuclear Export Factors TAP and Aly Are Required for HDAg-L-mediated 
Assembly of Hepatitis Delta Virus.

Huang HC(1), Lee CP(2), Liu HK(3)(4), Chang MF(5), Lai YH(6), Lee YC(7)(8), 
